  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In POROTO, a chaotic arcade adventure, restore order by blasting red 'Chaos orbs' in action-packed platforming! Jump and run across vibrant levels, strategically bouncing and shooting to <strong>eliminate all the red chaos</strong> in each level.  Earn ammo by <strong>collecting tiles</strong> or filling your <strong>combo meter</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master <strong>platforms that bounce, rotate, and vanish</strong>! Utilize <strong>power-ups like high jump and piercing shots</strong> to conquer challenging levels. Face <strong>epic boss fights</strong> that break the mold.  Embrace the chaos... to control it!  Fun mechanics, bite-sized levels, and a pumping soundtrack make POROTO an unforgettable experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676810/extras/13b2b3f75bc76efba72bd25aded170b3.poster.avif?t=1759846811\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676810/extras/13b2b3f75bc76efba72bd25aded170b3.webm?t=1759846811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676810/extras/13b2b3f75bc76efba72bd25aded170b3.mp4?t=1759846811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i>EMBRACE THE CHAOS</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676810/extras/04d866c887e129a0c4acc42a1f7fe4c8.poster.avif?t=1759846811\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676810/extras/04d866c887e129a0c4acc42a1f7fe4c8.webm?t=1759846811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676810/extras/04d866c887e129a0c4acc42a1f7fe4c8.mp4?t=1759846811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i>COLLECT POWERUPS FOR DIFFERENT ABILITIES</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676810/extras/21545b484dbaf7834e866dbac55181cd.poster.avif?t=1759846811\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676810/extras/21545b484dbaf7834e866dbac55181cd.webm?t=1759846811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676810/extras/21545b484dbaf7834e866dbac55181cd.mp4?t=1759846811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>FACE CHAOS ITSELF!</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In POROTO, a chaotic arcade adventure, restore order by blasting red 'Chaos orbs' in action-packed platforming! Jump and run across vibrant levels, strategically bouncing and shooting to <strong>eliminate all the red chaos</strong> in each level.  Earn ammo by <strong>collecting tiles</strong> or filling your <strong>combo meter</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master <strong>platforms that bounce, rotate, and vanish</strong>! Utilize <strong>power-ups like high jump and piercing shots</strong> to conquer challenging levels. Face <strong>epic boss fights</strong> that break the mold.  Embrace the chaos... to control it!  Fun mechanics, bite-sized levels, and a pumping soundtrack make POROTO an unforgettable experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676810/extras/13b2b3f75bc76efba72bd25aded170b3.poster.avif?t=1759846811\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676810/extras/13b2b3f75bc76efba72bd25aded170b3.webm?t=1759846811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676810/extras/13b2b3f75bc76efba72bd25aded170b3.mp4?t=1759846811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i>EMBRACE THE CHAOS</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676810/extras/04d866c887e129a0c4acc42a1f7fe4c8.poster.avif?t=1759846811\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2676810/extras/04d866c887e129a0c4acc42a1f7fe4c8.w